 answers some frequently asked questions
 
 q why montreal canadiens called habs
 most team during s made up people who lived 
 around montreal hence were called les habitants natives 
montreal shortened habs
 
 q why montreal canadiens logo large c h within 
 canadiens logo consisted c within 
signify club athletique canadien cac next year cac longer 
existed changed what now signify club de hockey

 q what most informative hockey publication
 hockey news preferred most north american hockey fans 
 weekly journal uptodate info
phone canada us
phonefax uk rest europe
 
 q how does minute powerplay count penalty killing stats 
 nhl
 x goals scored team gets credit x goals x 
chances
 
 q how computed nhl
 first only applies skaters except powerplay goal when 
 goal scored each skater ice scoring team given 
 each skater ice other team given short
handed goals do count 
 
 q what fivehole
 space between goalies pads five major scoring zones 
 upper left corner goal upper right lower left lower 
right fivehole
 
 q what meaning throwing octopus ice
 tradition began detroit s when two bestofseven 
series were required win stanley cup every time detroit won 
game octopus one less arm thrown ice

 q who first woman play nhl game
 manon rheaume yearold goaltender became first woman ever 
 play nhl game september when she started net 
 expansion tampa bay lightning exhibition against st louis 
blues rheaume played first period before seat 
expo hall florida state fairgrounds allowed two goals nine 
shots she left score tied although lightning ultimately 
lost game 

 q what richest contract nhl history
 mario lemieux superstar center pittsburgh penguins signed 
 richest contract nhl history sevenyear deal believed 
worth about million lemieux earn between million 
million year nearly twice much any other player league

 q who new commissioner nhl
 gary bettman vice president general counsel national 
basketball association named commissioner national hockey 
league friday december bettman joined nba 
assistant general counsel he became leagues chief legal officer 
september new york resident bettman graduated from cornell 
university from new york university school law 

 q how many professional hockey leagues north america
 six national american international east coast central 
colonial hockey leagues


 
